graph TD
    User([User / Factory Manager]) --> NextJS[Next.js 15 Dashboard]
    NextJS --> FastAPI[FastAPI Backend]
    FastAPI --> LangGraph[LangGraph Agent Orchestrator]

    subgraph Agent Society
        LangGraph --> Exec[Executive Agent]
        Exec <--> Prod[Production Agent]
        Exec <--> Inv[Inventory Agent]
        Exec <--> Proc[Procurement Agent]
        Exec <--> Qual[Quality Agent]
    end

    subgraph Memory & Context
        LangGraph <--> Mem[Memory Agent]
        Mem <--> PgVector[(PostgreSQL + pgvector)]
    end

    subgraph External LLM
        Exec <--> Qwen[Qwen Cloud APIs]
        Prod <--> Qwen
        Inv <--> Qwen
        Proc <--> Qwen
        Qual <--> Qwen
        Mem <--> Qwen
    end
